# Styling & Design System Rules

## CRITICAL: Design Token Usage

### Mandatory Rules
- **NEVER** use hardcoded colors - ALWAYS use CSS variables from `styles/design-tokens.css`
- **NEVER** use hardcoded spacing values - ALWAYS use spacing variables
- **NEVER** use inline styles unless absolutely necessary (e.g., dynamic JS-driven values)
- **NEVER** use `px` values directly - use design token variables

