## Accessibility Checklist

When using these colors:
- ✅ Text on yellow background MUST be black/dark
- ✅ Yellow should NOT be used for body text
- ✅ All interactive elements need focus states
- ✅ Contrast ratio minimum 4.5:1 for normal text
- ✅ Contrast ratio minimum 3:1 for large text (18px+)
- ✅ Don't rely on color alone - use icons/text too

